a-axonal injection of {HRP} or Neurobiotin. Labeled low-{CF} axons (N = 7), which were all high-sync, originated from {AVCN} bushy cells: five were globular and two were spherical bushy cell axons. 6. Spontaneous rate of high-sync fibers covered a range from 0 to 176 spikes/s but were biased toward low values (mean 16 spikes/s). Responses to broadband clicks and sinusoidally amplitude-modulated signals provided additional evidence of improved timing properties.({ABSTRACT} {TRUNCATED} {AT} 400 {WORDS})},
